MACWCP IV, LLC, PLaintiff-Respondent,
v.
MOTIVA ENTERPRISES, LLC, and State of New Jersey, Defendants,
and
Liberty Realty and Management, LLC, Defendant/Intervenor-Petitioner. C-781 September Term 2017
080647 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003640-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
